(网页点击缩放)，以及四项设计专利<a href="http://www.google.com/patents?id=6BsWAAAAEBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=D504,889&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=jR21wzKuTX&amp;sig=e9FuOUGGfybIdkflYLWShtj8xjk&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=Pug7UO7MFOy6yAGy3ICwBQ&amp;ved=0CDAQ6AEwAA">D504,889</a>
(矩形电子设备),
<a href="http://www.google.com/patents?id=-AbHAAAAEBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=D593,087&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=uBmFtc1dnn&amp;sig=DhMaRVneONjEocNdp611EfbkwGU&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=hug7UOH3Bu3ryAGxvoGQBQ&amp;ved=0CDAQ6AEwAA">D593,087</a>
(同上)、
<a href="http://www.google.com/patents?id=bRvVAAAAEBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=D618,677&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=eekgOO5mDC&amp;sig=cZUn0vCCqsvGXbXjkwja9Fe9XuY&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=u-g7UNXkDKaUywG1o4HgBA&amp;ved=0CDAQ6AEwAA">D618,677</a>
